-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
LIKE A ROLLING STONE – The Jimi Hendrix Experience
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Tabbed by: Andy and Others 
Email: None

Tuning: Half tone down
This is one of the best songs I’d ever heard. This is way I play it. I learned
it from different tabs so you may recognize something.

